apple_store_app_description:
Trader's Diary; trading journal; trading diary; portfolio tracker - these are all different names for one tool, the technological version of which is optimally embodied in the Letit Tracker application.

The innovative mobile application “Letit Tracker” is designed for traders of all skill levels who want to analyze their trading operations on the futures and spot markets. “Letit Tracker” - optimizes the process of self-control for both beginners and professionals, maintains a detailed and structured history of transactions, providing the user with valuable analytics of trading activities and analysis of the investment portfolio.

Main functions:
  • Automatic collection of data about user activities on exchanges: The application itself collects information about the user’s transactions and operations on the market. "Letit Tracker" is absolutely safe as it only uses "read API keys".
  • Groups and organizes exchange activity data in a convenient and easy-to-read form with intuitive graphs and charts.
  • Storage and analysis of trading history. The application displays in detail your trading history and all the trades you have executed on different markets.
  • Cryptocurrency rates: Letit Tracker provides up-to-date and accurate data on cryptocurrency rates, allowing you to monitor market changes in real time.
  • Accrual of bonuses: “Letit Tracker” automatically accrues cashback to users in the amount of 10% from exchange commissions. The more active the user is in trading, the greater the bonus.

With their help:

  ⁃ Evaluate the effectiveness of different strategies;
  ⁃ Make decisions based on analysis of trading history;
  ⁃ Track the dynamics of your profit;
  ⁃ Avoid repeating mistakes based on transaction analytics;
  ⁃ Save time on manual diary keeping,
  ⁃ Eliminate the human factor when filling out data;
  ⁃ Connect several exchanges to diversify your portfolio;
  ⁃ Manage your investment portfolio effectively and maximize profits.
  ⁃ Get up-to-date data on cryptocurrency rates;
  ⁃ Get a return on 10% exchange commissions.

Make your trading operations more meaningful and successful, earn more with the Letit Tracker application. Download the app now and start effectively analyzing your trades today!
